Available Tools: get_temperature | get_humidity | get_wind_speed | get_uv_index
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "location": "string", "unit": "celsius|fahrenheit" }
Response Schema: { "value": number, "unit": "string", "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: What is the temperature in Berlin right now in Celsius?
Call: { "func_call": "get_temperature", "location": "Berlin", "unit": "celsius" }
Response: { "value": 9.4, "unit": "celsius", "timestamp": "2023-10-28T11:20:00Z" }

Question: How hot is it in Dubai? Please use Fahrenheit.
Call: { "func_call": "get_temperature", "location": "Dubai", "unit": "fahrenheit" }
Response: { "value": 95.6, "unit": "fahrenheit", "timestamp": "2023-10-28T14:45:00Z" }

Question: Give me the current temperature for Singapore in Celsius.
Call: { "func_call": "get_temperature", "location": "Singapore", "unit": "celsius" }
Response: { "value": 28.7, "unit": "celsius", "timestamp": "2023-10-28T19:30:00Z" }

